gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 122, Wizards 119
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Wizards in OT. Cam Thomas led the Nets with 38 points and seven assists as Jordan Poole totaled a season-high 38 points and seven rebounds, along with eight assists in the loss. The Nets move to 28-45 as the Wizards have their 3-game win streak snapped to move to 14-59.
